Class Container

  • java.lang.Object
    • entityPackage.Entity
      • entityPackage.Container
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Entity>

    public class Container
extends Entity
    A container is a collection of instances of the Entity class. it exports capabilities of the ArrayList Class, an update and a render function. Since Container extends Entity, a container can contain other containers.

    watacoso
